<name key="安丙" type="givenName">丙</name>遂如<placeName>果州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>時<num value="4">四</num>川大震<pc>，</pc>甚於曦之變<pc>。</pc>張方首奏<pc>，</pc>勳望如<name key="安丙" type="givenName">丙</name>
<pc>，</pc>今猶可用<pc>。</pc>魏了翁移書宰執<pc>，</pc>謂安<name key="安丙" type="givenName">丙</name>不起<pc>，</pc>則賊未即平<pc>，</pc>蜀未可定<pc>，</pc>雖賊亦曰<pc>：</pc>
